        "In this **Natural Join**, we are joining on two columns that both tables have in common: `BusID` and `DriverID`. The join automatically combines rows where both the `BusID` **and** `DriverID` match. This natural join will return only rows where both the bus and passenger data have matching `BusID` and `DriverID`. In this case, it will exclude any buses or passengers where these two columns do not match simultaneously.\n",
